What you need to know:  Making the changes through a Kenya Gazette notice on Friday, Cabinet Secretary for Sports Ababu Namwamba said that members of both the Steering Committee and Organising Committee will serve one year starting January 4, this yearNamwamba will be the chairperson of the Steering Committee and will be deputised by the Principal Secretary for Sports Jonathan MuekeKenya Motor Sports Federation (KMSF) chairman Phineas Kimathi is the secretary of the Steering Committee that will also have several members